### GREEN Verification Results

**Test:** Query CISA KEV catalog for Apache vulnerabilities
**URL:** `https://www.cisa.gov/known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog?search_api_fulltext=apache&...`
**Result:** Successfully extracted 5 CVEs with all required fields:
- CVE-2024-38475 (Apache HTTP Server RCE)
- CVE-2025-24813 (Apache Tomcat RCE)
- CVE-2017-3066 (Adobe ColdFusion/BlazeDS RCE)
- CVE-2024-45195 (Apache OFBiz Forced Browsing)
- CVE-2024-27348 (Apache HugeGraph RCE)

### Skill Complete

**Status:** Ready for use
